{"article_id":"3vEAHxSLgFDavHiV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The U.S. Supreme Court has declined to block controversial Texas abortion restrictions","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that have been called some of the strictest in the country","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"and have led a dozen abortion clinics in the state to stop performing the procedure .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"The court by a 5-4 vote denied a request by Planned Parenthood","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"to block a ruling by the 5th Circuit Court of Appeals ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"allowing key parts of the Texas abortion law to stay in effect","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"while the lawsuit","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"challenging the restrictions","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"moves forward .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"The four liberal justices","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"who voted in favor of the request said","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"they would have overturned the appeals court 's Oct. 31 ruling","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that allowed the law to take effect .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"In its 20-page ruling , the panel of appeals court judges acknowledged","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"that the law 's provision","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"requiring doctors to have admitting privileges at a nearby hospital","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"`` may increase the cost","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"of accessing an abortion provider","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"and decrease the number of physicians","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"available to perform abortions . ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"However , the panel said","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that the U.S. Supreme Court has held","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that having `` the incidental effect","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"of making it more difficult or more expensive to procure an abortion","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"can not be enough","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"to invalidate '' a law","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that serves a valid purpose , `` one","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"not designed","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"to strike at the right itself . ''","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"The provision has led at least 12 clinics in the state to stop performing abortions since the ruling .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"A spokeswoman for the Texas Attorney General 's Office said Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"the office is `` pleased '' with the Supreme Court 's ruling .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"`` These are commonsense","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"- and perfectly constitutional -","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"regulations","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"that further the state 's interest","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"in protecting the health and safety of Texas women , ''","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Lauren Bean said .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Republican Texas Gov . Rick Perry also said","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"he was happy with the court 's decision .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"`` This is good news both for the unborn and for the women of Texas ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"who are now better protected from shoddy abortion providers","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"operating in dangerous conditions , ''","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Perry said .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"The appeals court panel left in place a portion of a previous judge 's order","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that prevents the state from enforcing the U.S. Food and Drug Administration protocol for abortion-inducing drugs in cases","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"where the woman is between 50 and 63 days into her pregnancy .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Doctors","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"testifying before the court","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"had said","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"such women would be harmed","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"if the protocol were enforced .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"The appeals court 's order is temporary","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"until it can hold a complete hearing , likely in January .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"The restrictions gained notoriety","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"when Democratic state Sen. Wendy Davis launched a nearly 13-hour filibuster against them in June .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"The law also bans abortions after 20 weeks of pregnancy","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"and","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"beginning in October 2014","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"requires doctors to perform all abortions in surgical facilities .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"During the trial , officials for one chain of abortion clinics testified","depth":5},{"id":62,"text":"that they 've tried to obtain admitting privileges for their doctors at 32 hospitals ,","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"but so far only 15 accepted applications","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"and none have announced a decision .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Many hospitals with religious affiliations will not allow abortion doctors to work there ,","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"while others fear protests","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"if they provide privileges .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Many have requirements","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"that doctors live within a certain radius of the facility ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"or perform a minimum number of surgeries a year","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"that must be performed in a hospital .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Fox News ' Shannon Bream and The Associated Press contributed to this report","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":145,"left":144,"right":72,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":129,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":102,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":85,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":75,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":0,"right":74,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":1,"right":2,"